modName: Casual bikini and shoes gloves stockings UNP UNPB CBBE ADEC - DELETED
summary:
returning of my old mod
bikini, shoes, gloves, stockings
descriptionHtml:
-----------------------------Description-----------------------------
It is returning of my old mod
Mod has variants for UNP, UNPB BBP, CBBE, ADEC BBP version

Mod has 30 variants of each bikini, bikinitops, bikinibottoms
(tops and full bikini use slot 32, bikinibottom uses slot 52)

32 variants of each gloves and stockings
(stockings use slot 54)

12 variants of shoes
Also mod contains item called "A Naked body" - it is naked body
(Added this item because CBBE ADEC UNPB versions uses old body versions)

Also mod contains few piercings and necklaces

Bikini, shoes, stockings, gloves, piercings, necklaces can be found in chests in Whiterun
near gates and Warmaiden (Whiterun blacksmith shop) - look screens
Also bikini, necklaces, piercings can be bought in Warmaiden from new vendor.
Shoes, gloves, stockings can be crafterd and tempered in leather section.
Necklaces and piercings can be crafted in jewellery section.

Also mod contains optional file that deletes shoes gloves stockings from craft menu.
Another optional file adds bikini to craft and temper sections.

Color versions:
bikini:
Black, blackwhite, blacknet, chess, darknet, darktransparent, blue, bluewhite, deepgreen,
deepurple, deepred, greenwhite, lightblue, olive, orange, pink, pinkwhite, purpwhite,
red, redwhite, rednet, slaaneshblack, slaaneshred (2), white, whitenet, whitetransparent,
whitefishnet, yellow, yellowhite.

gloves and stockings:
blackfull, slaaneshblack, slaaneshred, net and transparent:
black, blue, brown, darkred, red, deepgreen, deepblue, deeppurp,
green, lightblue, olive, pink, purp, white, yellow.

shoes:
black(2), blue, darkred (2), darkpurp, green, milkcoffee,
pink, purple, red, white

PS. Does NOT require HDT high heels or NiOverride.
You can download also my another bikini mod [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70477]Chain bikini and heels gloves stockings[/url]
